basics.summary:
Welcome!

This is my personal portfolio, as well as a hosting page for various things I code, write, and imagine.

About me: I was born in 1993 in Hungary and during the years I have extensive creative endeavours, from creating gameplay-commentary videos on Youtube, to writing, to level design until I settled down with coding.

Programming is the biggest passion of my life.
